#if soper
Command provided by: nickserv/set_notifymemo
#endif
Help for SET NOTIFYMEMO:

If enabled, receive a memo whenever your group or
channel settings in channels where you're on the ACL
changes.  NOTIFYACL and/or NOTIFYSET must also be
enabled.

Syntax: SET NOTIFYMEMO [ON|OFF]

Example:
    /msg &nick& SET NOTIFYMEMO ON